---
title: BBQ Beef Cheeseburgers with Golden Potato Coins
description: Tonight, you can have BBQ-inspired flavours, without turning on the grill! Slicing potatoes into coins helps to speed up their roast time for a quick, delicious dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-au-fromage-et-au-boeuf-bbq-d2df0ad6.jpg
